Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,兵分两路吧 薇薇和李奥纳多从右边绕到前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:51.42,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,食物 掉落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:52.59,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:04.34,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,基列特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.35,Default,Leonardo,0,0,0,,这里没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.80,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,以这一片为中心再找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:09.78,Default,All,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.64,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,只是装饰品吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.52,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.04,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是剧场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.88,Default,Leonardo,0,0,0,,没有躲进 附近的房屋和商店的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.76,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,要藏身的话就只有躲进这间剧场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.10,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,哦 看啊 这剑的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.42,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,会将正义之刃收入其中的是我速度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.52,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,还是敌人的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:55.99,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,来吧 站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.36,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,戏剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.32,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,棺材？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:06.95,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,上吧 打倒禁断皇帝贾兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.12,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.96,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,好像是“讨伐贾兹皇帝”的戏剧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:13.38,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁 我想要看戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.46,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,别闹了 会被发现的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:18.76,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,除了等戏剧结束 混在观众里一起离开之外就没别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.70,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,这…很难办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.44,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,贼人已入侵的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.47,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,难道不应该暂时中止表演吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.31,OPEDEG,Toru,0,0,0,,这个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:32.97,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,今晚的戏剧是专门为领主大人以及亲族准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:35.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,一旦中止了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,领主大人就颜面无存了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.03,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,总之你先藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.07,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,听好了 在我回来之前都不许出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁 什么时候回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 先找个藏身的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.71,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,既然戏剧不能中止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就在不影响观众的前提下搜索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.38,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,要把观众的安全放在第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:03:59.67,Default,All,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.84,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是化妆室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.18,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,哎呀 让一让 让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.73,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,完了 这样就无法行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.03,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,嗯 托鲁他们就在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.57,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.71,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.75,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,这里就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.00,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,人真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.01,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,虽然 我不认为他们会躲在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.30,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,不过不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.43,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,乱破师这种人为了钻空子什么都干得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:53.02,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,舞者们 化完妆以后赶紧到后台准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.44,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.66,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,你们两个怎么还是这副打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:04:59.90,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,不…我们并不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.32,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,赶紧换衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.07,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,观众们可不会等的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.07,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,等她们出去了再进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.45,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这些家伙…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,差不多要等到第三幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.25,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,【幼主】吗 额…啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:20.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,好嘞 搬走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.13,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,嘿咻~~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.43,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,来 赶紧的 赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.89,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.14,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,这个忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.27,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不得了 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.09,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,你在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:51.79,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,街上停着基列特队的车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:56.25,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,你们买东西又没回来我还以为你们被他们找上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:06:00.00,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,没想到你居然是为了解放隐藏的性癖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.18,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,等等 阿卡莉 先听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.75,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,不要想当然 兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.64,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,有穿女装的兴趣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然会有各种各样的亲近办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:13.54,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,但唯一的问题是 该叫兄长大人呢 还是姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.22,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,听我说啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.19,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,果然是因为基列特队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.55,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:22.67,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我是想着不论如何都要撑到戏剧演完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.84,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,托鲁 你看着可傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.41,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡和棺材不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.63,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:33.16,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,终于打倒了贾兹皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:35.69,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,来 将棺材搬到这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:41.88,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,来吧 这是庆祝的宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.63,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,起舞吧 起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.26,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,停止 要求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.26,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嘉依卡就在那里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.10,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.02,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,按照剧情走向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来像是要打开棺材安放遗体了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.95,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,强抢了就跑 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:07.89,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,基列特队也在 闹起来的话宪兵队会冲过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.82,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我可不觉得能跑得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:11.19,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.62,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,怎么样 合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.75,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:21.49,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,打扮成这样攻略基列特大人试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.83,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,你…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.01,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉 芷依塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.92,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,薇薇 看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.34,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,是那个乱破师的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.77,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,来吧 将这不详的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,收入棺材之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:39.01,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,打开这具棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:43.56,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.15,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,啊 赶上了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:53.18,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,打到了皇帝 恶意的诅咒解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:57.37,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,被封印的女神终于要复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:58.33,Default,Both,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.88,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,女神大人万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:03.55,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,来吧 大家一同迎接她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:07.92,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,和平女神 嘉依…嘉依曼努西大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:12.59,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依曼努西大人 请在我们面前现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.25,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.23,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,配合我们的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.31,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,请把 嘉依曼努西大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:35.02,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我是…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.66,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,女神 嘉依曼努西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.49,Default,Both,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.25,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,什么玩意 我怎么不知道有女神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.66,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,会不会是领主大人来了所以改剧本了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.75,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,总之先配合着演下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.33,Default,All,0,0,0,,嘉依曼努西大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.13,Default,Both,0,0,0,,嘉依曼努西万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.61,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,哦 真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.61,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,就像是真的女神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:58.35,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.30,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,尼克拉 舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.99,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,观众席就交给李奥纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.86,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.44,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,大大方方登上舞台倒是让我出乎意料了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.19,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,不过闹剧已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.95,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,你们逃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:19.46,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,禁断皇帝的女儿嘉依卡中的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:22.33,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,你们的存在将成为战乱的火种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.33,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,乖乖跟我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:39.09,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,哎呀真是的 安德雷你喝醉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.97,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,真是磨人的小妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:47.02,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,真好笑 安德雷的玩笑话总是能让我笑个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:50.72,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,好了 把玩具一员的剑收起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.90,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,今夜可是女神大人复活的庆典哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.15,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.65,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,什么情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:00.24,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 达尼尔大叔也来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.12,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,达尼尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:05.87,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,今天可不能喝太多掉进池塘里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.16,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,来吧 跳起舞来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.88,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,为女神大人献上热闹的宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.38,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,喂 去伴舞 去伴舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.71,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,等一等…你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.97,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,这可不是演戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:19.22,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.66,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,等等趁着乱赶紧逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:22.22,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.70,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,基列特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.85,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,不要让嘉依卡跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.02,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,现身吧 漂浮之物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.98,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,<漂浮者>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:38.86,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.12,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,吾将红莲施舍予 引来火焰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.08,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,<燃烧者>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:07.00,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.56,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,这根本不是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.60,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.30,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:12.19,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,喂 谢幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.81,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,这并不是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.73,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,快逃 快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:25.16,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,这好像是家有几百年历史的剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:29.26,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,战争中也奇迹般地保存了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.75,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 反省
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:35.00,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,剧场 失火 我深刻反省
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.53,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,与你无关啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:18.80,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.09,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.97,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,有那个骑士的同伴在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:26.92,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:31.53,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,在街上听到的传闻未必就是假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:34.92,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,遗体 就在附近的希沙姆遗迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:38.11,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄长大人 落在那些家伙后面就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.53,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.04,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 稍微麻烦你下行不？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.15,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.62,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,逃掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.70,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,被那个女乱破师偷袭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.83,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:59.70,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,在被攻击之前好像看到了什么非常美好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.21,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,可我却想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:07.09,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,基列特大人 那些家伙应该瞄上了希沙姆遗迹中的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:10.06,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,嗯 快点去比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.27,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,遗体 绝对不会让出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.27,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,就是那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.81,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,根据传言 遗体好像就在那座圣堂里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.24,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:32.68,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,闻着传言的味道来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:35.12,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,可惜你们已经到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.71,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.26,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.40,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,遗体 不让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.43,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.29,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.78,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.04,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,为什么 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.61,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.28,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,放手 立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.02,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,为什么你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.67,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,塞尔玛和大卫在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.03,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.56,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我还想问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:26.84,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可恶 嘉依卡在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.01,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嘉依卡是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.10,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:33.81,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不是说你 是说白色的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:40.12,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,喂 你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.52,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,不要你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.48,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,敌人的同情不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.28,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.54,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,下落中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:15:00.90,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,等我从这里出去一定会抓捕你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:04.13,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,但现在从这里出去才是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.88,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,来把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.47,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,比起抓住你 放开绳子更难办到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.54,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,掉落的恐惧 很大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:14.92,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,但是这样下去你会掉进泥沼里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:15.57,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:17.35,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,从嘉依卡身旁离开！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.44,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,等着我 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.32,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我马上就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.48,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.44,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,来 嘉依卡 抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:33.18,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,不行 一旦放手 落进去的可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:42.45,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,喂 把手放开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.63,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,抱歉 那我可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.29,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,我可是打算在这里就抓住你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:50.63,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,呵呵 能办到的话你就试试看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.38,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,那两个家伙是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.80,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,放手啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.39,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,我两只手臂都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.10,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,真想帮她就放手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:05.61,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,笨蛋 哪有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.53,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,而且对我 直接攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.76,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,谁管你 亲妈什么的都是什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.89,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,你从头顶掉下来扯平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.98,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 满身泥浆 责任追究
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:18.88,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,满身泥浆 我 同样 扯平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:21.67,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:23.96,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,抓住这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:24.87,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,不会让你逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:26.38,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.64,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,这个 你想用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:31.14,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,拒绝使用 我自己解决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.13,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,你能 自己解决？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.36,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄长大人 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.43,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.30,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄长就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:37.65,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,拉我上去之前先干掉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:45.07,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,别这样 即便做了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:48.10,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,我的部下也会很快抓住你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:53.58,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,你们帮助这个小丫头也不会有什么好事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:55.12,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:56.97,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,简直像个小泥人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:05.93,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 你和嘉依卡一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:06.85,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:14.69,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:16.55,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,不用管我 抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.43,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,这次你们逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.39,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这可不好说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.60,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,别放手啊 李奥纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:37.87,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.91,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,活该啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:44.12,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,在我们拿到宝物之前你们就在泥沼里好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.01,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.17,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,放弃吧 完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.15,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.30,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,基列特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.34,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,薇薇 你们去追嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.09,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:57.26,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,薇薇来看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.22,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,哼 那些傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.51,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,等下 嘉依卡 这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.73,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,追踪线索 不可残留
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:14.82,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,马特乌斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:19.78,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:22.10,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,脚印只到这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.58,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,果然还是意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.30,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,走了哪一边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.70,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,兵分两路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:30.21,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,嗯 我和芷依塔从小路绕过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.04,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:39.21,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,这个遗迹好像被水路包围着的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:43.25,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,从这里开始游泳去圣堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.08,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.38,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,那家伙我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:02.76,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,你先去圣堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.66,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.01,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:54.12,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,圣堂 到达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.67,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,遗体 大概 在此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.26,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,你 果然 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:03.40,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,带路 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.97,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,遗体 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.93,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我不会让出遗体的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:10.52,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,没有机会 你一个人什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:18.40,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,辛苦了 遗体已经由我们两人回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.19,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,接下来只要抓住你们就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.32,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:39.30,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:39.88,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:42.13,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,这里是…圣堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.26,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.57,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,阿卡莉
